# 8. Design Tokens

Design tokens represent the smallest unit of design decisions.

Token categories include:

• color  
• typography  
• spacing  
• radius  
• elevation  
• motion  
• stroke  
• opacity  

Example token:

```json
{
  "color": {
    "accent": "#0078D4",
    "foregroundPrimary": "#1A1A1A"
  }
}
```

